    <item>
      <title>自库维德（Covid）以来，最严重的库存崩溃引发了全球衰退的恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/global-recession-trade-engulfs-wall-street-on-tariff-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在金融市场的每个角落，从股票到债券再到商品，投资者都向唐纳德·特朗普发出了同样的明确信息：他释放的贸易战争威胁要引发全球衰退＆mdash＆mdash;和快速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/global-recession-trade-engulfs-wall-street-on-tariff-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:27:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耐克，特朗普吹捧与越南领导人打电话的lululemon反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/nike-lululemon-soar-as-trump-touts-productive-call-with-vietnam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统表示，越南愿意取消关税以避免新的美国征费，在越南拥有大型制造业务的公司的股票，包括耐克公司和卢卢利蒙田径公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/nike-lululemon-soar-as-trump-touts-productive-call-with-vietnam</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大股票对特朗普关税的担忧予以更正</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/canadian-stocks-tumble-into-correction-as-trump-tariff-fears-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对主要贸易伙伴的关税引发了人们对经济衰退的担忧，加拿大股票陷入了更正领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/canadian-stocks-tumble-into-correction-as-trump-tariff-fears-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:44:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
