      <title>纳斯达克100人陷入熊市，因为特朗普关税火花溃败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-tariffs-drive-us-tech-shares-to-brink-of-bear-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克100号（NASDAQ 100）陷入了熊市，其损失从2月的高涨幅度飙升了20％，因为投资者曾在广泛的市场途中抛弃曾经飞行的技术股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-tariffs-drive-us-tech-shares-to-brink-of-bear-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:35:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
